Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.59,0:03:07.27,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,不相信有什么是绝对的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.46,0:03:10.13,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,没有什么是不可能的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.35,0:03:15.43,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)}未来就掌握在这只手中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.60,0:03:20.64,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,无论怎么做都无法战胜的恶魔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.94,0:03:25.74,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,老奸巨猾地装扮成女神的样子  (◎_◎;)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.44,0:03:31.25,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,只是因为经验值不够吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.78,0:03:37.26,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,250)}一生锻炼　在反复试验中认真琢磨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.66,0:03:42.16,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,愈是遇到难题就愈是摩拳擦掌跃跃欲试
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.73,0:03:46.87,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,能见到会心的笑容就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.97,0:03:52.74,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,我得到了藏宝图
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.61,0:03:58.94,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,无拘无束　带着你一同奋勇前进！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:02.00,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,快乐的误会
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.00,0:04:04.59,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,絕不动摇的誓言！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.87,0:04:09.84,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,我会改变风的去向给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.33,0:04:12.84,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,不要在意打扮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.84,0:04:15.67,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,命运就不会消沉！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.90,0:04:20.87,opzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)}宛如吹散浮云的旋风！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.12,0:21:49.13,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,笑着转啊转啊转
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.13,0:21:52.94,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,啦啦转啊转啊转　哪怕是哭泣的日子里
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.94,0:21:58.59,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,撩人的风中摇晃的笑脸　心情变得愉快
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.59,0:22:01.83,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,今天也转啊转啊转　到处转啊转啊转
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.83,0:22:13.06,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}阳光下一时兴起与你跳着舞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.48,0:22:21.07,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,被若无其事伸出的手所深深吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.39,0:22:27.66,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,连下一句话都弄的像迷路的孩子那样不知所措
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.66,0:22:32.61,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,被少年老成严实包裹着的目光里
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.83,0:22:37.76,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}渐渐忘却了逞强
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.20,0:22:44.32,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,在令人无眠的漫漫长夜中　请轻轻地摸摸我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.47,0:22:49.48,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,也请摸摸刚从睡意朦胧中苏醒的脸颊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.31,0:22:51.26,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,转啊转啊转
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.26,0:22:55.14,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1000)}啦啦转啊转啊转　摆着架子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.64,0:23:00.77,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,看吧　你的侧脸　在一瞬间　忍不住笑起来了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.77,0:23:04.01,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,与蓝天转啊转啊转　到处转啊转啊转
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.01,0:23:08.47,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,在你转动着的风中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.47,0:23:15.41,edzw,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,1500)}向着太阳跳起舞蹈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.02,0:00:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.67,0:00:03.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.01,0:00:08.75,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大～小～姐——！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.75,0:00:11.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…不在
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.95,0:00:15.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪  也不在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.44,0:00:17.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐去哪里了…嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.02,0:00:21.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.07,0:00:26.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,您…您是怎么了  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.40,0:00:29.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,前辈  请用这运动毛巾吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.24,0:00:32.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…会为你今天比赛加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.18,0:00:35.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比…比赛是？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.64,0:00:37.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:40.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐坏掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.40,0:00:43.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在小凪正在执笔新的漫画哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.20,0:00:45.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,漫画？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.51,0:00:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要挑战清新的青春爱情故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.54,0:00:49.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.86,0:00:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以为模仿角色就能以角色的心情流畅地画下去  不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.05,0:01:03.11,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行的  画不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.28,0:01:05.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你没事吧  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.76,0:01:08.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,直到中途还感觉不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.07,0:01:09.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,感觉不错？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:12.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  感觉不错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.13,0:01:17.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爱上在圣山学院传统强项部的队长沃索托加迪·查滔的\N女主角意普里斯亚思·伸惠
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.37,0:01:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在经历了多次与男主角擦肩而过之后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.90,0:01:21.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,终于迎来了初次与查滔约会的这一幕
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.46,0:01:23.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但是却不知道如何下笔才好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.85,0:01:27.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…那真的是清新青春爱情故事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.43,0:01:28.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有点乱七八糟啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.36,0:01:33.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么  为什么本是天才的我居然会画不下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.26,0:01:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀…不要钻牛角尖了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.26,0:01:35.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.13,0:01:37.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为没有资料才画不下去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.53,0:01:39.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.54,0:01:41.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.87,0:01:42.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.48,0:01:44.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在马上就去给我收集资料吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.58,0:01:46.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,资…资料指？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:50.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你用这照相机把现今年轻人喜欢的约会地点给拍下来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.57,0:01:56.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…不过  现在的约会地点什么的我是一点都不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.35,0:02:00.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你是想说「别啰啰嗦嗦  这可是主人的大事  快点去」吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.24,0:02:04.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.88,0:02:07.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,约会什么的我一次都没有过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.03,0:02:10.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这已经是最近很少见的年轻人了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.24,0:02:11.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:12.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好的  不管你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.50,0:02:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯…去哪里比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:18.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说到约会该去原宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.25,0:02:19.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,都说了别管我了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.71,0:02:20.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原宿
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:25.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…那个…那个那个那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.31,0:02:27.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难…难道…难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.88,0:02:29.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是玛莉亚小姐？！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:30.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:34.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为穿着便服我一时没有认出来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.62,0:02:37.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还…还以为是哪里的贵妇人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.98,0:02:40.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我偶尔也会穿这种衣服的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.10,0:02:43.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说回来  我也可以陪你一起去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.31,0:02:52.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能征服管家界的人就能征服世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.34,0:02:57.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在让地球为之动摇的管家大战即将开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:02:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,和玛莉亚小姐约会？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.85,0:03:03.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈哈  是吗  这回的故事就像做梦一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.24,0:03:04.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没错  一定是这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.46,0:04:38.98,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,0)\fscx80}必看！给现今年轻人的\N最新最时尚的约会地点完全指导2007秋季版
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:40.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.90,0:04:43.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  是大小姐说想一人待着吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.20,0:04:45.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.14,0:04:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是回想吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.48,0:04:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还真是麻烦您了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.29,0:04:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…行…啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:53.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么都画不出
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.84,0:04:56.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道了  一定是因为有人我才无法集中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:59.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人？  指…指我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.21,0:05:01.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玛莉亚  今天你可以休息了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.35,0:05:02.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也这样告诉克劳斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.62,0:05:04.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我想一个人待着
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:07.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,克劳斯先生？  其实…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.45,0:05:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说三千院家有各种各样的人在工作
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.70,0:05:15.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,但主宅里却没有人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.44,0:05:17.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因为小凪讨厌佣人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:19.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.95,0:05:21.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最后的画面完全是个迷…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.06,0:05:24.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在叫人去收集资料之后是支开旁人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.78,0:05:26.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就像漫画热卖的作者一样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.44,0:05:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,突然说让我放假  不过我也没有什么特别的事情要做
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:32.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:34.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就来陪一下小飒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:38.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交～往～？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.87,0:05:38.03,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,（日文「陪同」与「交往」同音）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,交…交…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.64,0:05:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给你添麻烦了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:46.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不会不会…像我这样的人居然能与玛莉亚小姐交往…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.85,0:05:51.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想帮你替小凪收集资料
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:54.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是这种意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.52,0:05:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:05:58.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！很顺利  很顺利
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.22,0:06:00.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有精神了吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.25,0:06:00.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:03.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,突然放我假也太不讲理了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.64,0:06:05.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我这把岁数了可没地方去…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.91,0:06:06.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.85,0:06:09.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去游戏中心或者网吧总能把一天消耗掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别哭了  克劳斯  都一把岁数了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.33,0:06:14.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太丢脸了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.43,0:06:18.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  都是情侣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.17,0:06:21.33,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（白衣服的男生是「机动战士高达Z」的主角卡缪）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:22.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,情侣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:24.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.01,0:06:26.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…难道是因为习惯了宅院里的生活了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.14,0:06:27.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有点头晕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:30.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  为了大小姐得好好收集资料
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.89,0:06:32.65,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（这两位是「机动战士Z高达」的柯特罗和哈曼）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.75,0:06:33.53,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（两个女生是「ToHeart2」的瑠璃和珊瑚，中间的男生是河野贵明）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.80,0:06:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  下面去哪里拍比较好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:41.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不能错过竹下大道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.22,0:06:42.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,竹下大道？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.51,0:06:44.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我没记错的话
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:46.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,首先入口有充满精神的House
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:50.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其它还有Tunnels的情人节House  芳贺隆之和酒井法子之类的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:50.69,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（Tunnels：石桥贵明和木梨宪武的艺人组合，1981年出道）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:50.69,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（芳贺隆之：1977年开始出道歌坛，昵称所ジョージ(所George)或所さん）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.18,0:06:50.69,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（酒井法子的「のりピー语」为80年代偶像用语）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.86,0:06:53.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…那是什么时代的事情了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:55.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  那里有过去有名的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.98,0:06:59.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～不行  这个就算加了「哔」音也会NG的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.40,0:07:01.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪  都没了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.03,0:07:05.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  是不是很早之前就没了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.62,0:07:09.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正如多次强调的  玛莉亚是朝气蓬勃的17岁少女
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:12.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  还好带了指导手册
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.25,0:07:14.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在这附近逛一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:17.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  玛莉亚小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玛莉亚小姐  难道你想看衣服吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.81,0:07:23.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.49,0:07:25.13,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,才不是呢  真讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:28.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我完全没有对最新流行感兴趣或者想穿最近时髦的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:31.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还有最喜欢打扮什么的这样的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.53,0:07:32.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.68,0:07:35.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  看起来也能成为大小姐的参考资料
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.61,0:07:38.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说…说得也是  真没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.69,0:07:39.82,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那  就稍微看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.01,0:07:40.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.57,0:07:45.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒  快看  有这么多可爱的衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.82,0:07:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这连衣裙很畅销哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:49.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请慢慢欣赏吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:53.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玛莉亚小姐果然也是普通的女孩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:54.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:54.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.56,0:08:00.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒  我可以试穿一下吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.55,0:08:03.15,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（「乱马」1/2里风林馆高中的校服）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.06,0:08:05.69,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（「蔷薇少女」中水银灯，两人声优都是田中理惠）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.46,0:08:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个简直…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.13,0:08:07.26,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（「宇宙刑警Shaider」中阿尼的服装）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.74,0:08:08.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.03,0:08:10.57,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（店员是柳原加奈子，日本的搞笑艺人）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.35,0:08:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真碍事  走开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.30,0:08:14.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.32,0:08:15.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,每一件都非常适合
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.14,0:08:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.19,0:08:21.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在开始请叫我  「动漫界的小虾」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,得意忘形了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.75,0:08:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:24.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是  是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:25.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是很适合吗  不是很漂亮吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.65,0:08:27.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喏  那边的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.93,0:08:30.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,男…男…男朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.17,0:08:31.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也来试穿看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.61,0:08:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,能行的  一定会很合适的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:38.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  太漂亮了  真的很合适啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:41.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.22,0:08:43.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最高了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.89,0:08:45.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Nice Couple啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.23,0:08:47.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总觉得很不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:49.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,伤…伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.03,0:08:52.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太好吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.73,0:08:54.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,果然来了原宿就该吃这个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.26,0:08:56.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过太无聊了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.72,0:08:58.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,除了Crepe之外都没有其它令人心动的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:03.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为雪路说原宿存在着边跳舞边卖竹笋的民族才来的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.08,0:09:05.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:07.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那是竹笋族
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.26,0:09:11.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便一提  不知道竹笋族的人去问一下旁边的大人或者玛莉亚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:13.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.85,0:09:15.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,吃了这个就回学校睡个午觉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.12,0:09:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  明明才刚出来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:20.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且我们的出场只有三个镜头
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:25.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么令人心跳的事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.66,0:09:27.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  有了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:29.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对…对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.24,0:09:32.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,结果  还顺带连我的衣服都买了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:33.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没…没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:35.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.17,0:09:36.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那怎么看都让人羡慕的情侣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.03,0:09:38.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那不是我们的「好朋友」哈亚太吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.06,0:09:41.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到哈亚太居然有那么漂亮的女朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.30,0:09:43.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  那是小凪家的女仆吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:44.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦！穿上便服就认不出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.64,0:09:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是说  这是管家与女佣间的「Love in 原宿」吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:51.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦  这样的话  我们就让他们的约会气氛更加高涨吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:56.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,告诉学生如何纯洁正确地进行男女交往  也是教师的工作啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.73,0:09:59.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还说什么工作  明明只是想玩乐而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:00.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  这可是相当的有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.94,0:10:02.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呐呐  如果两人要是结婚的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.86,0:10:04.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们能去致辞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.15,0:10:07.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,何止致辞  我们可是贵宾  要干杯个够！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,Dom Perignon整瓶吞啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:08.99,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（Moet et Chandon公司生产的一款香槟）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.14,0:10:10.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因此  大家上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:12.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,上啦上啦上啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.44,0:10:18.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,呃…感觉有点尴尬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.41,0:10:21.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这种时候说什么才好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.33,0:10:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,刚…刚才的店员说我们是情侣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.82,0:10:28.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真不可思议  居然是情侣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.52,0:10:34.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说回来  本来…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.01,0:10:37.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,有必要这么心跳吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:38.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:43.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要…要在这附近给大小姐拍照片
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:45.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说…说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:47.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不介意的话  给你们拍一张吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.63,0:10:49.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是变装吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:51.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过戴了个爆炸头
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.75,0:10:55.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是破坏了原宿唯美气氛的爆炸头众吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.32,0:10:57.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请问  你们是？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.25,0:11:00.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,正如你所见  是超天才摄影师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.13,0:11:01.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,以及她的助手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.46,0:11:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总感觉不是初次见面的人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.80,0:11:06.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是前世有缘的人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.05,0:11:09.50,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,两人因为太紧张了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.57,0:11:12.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么简单的变装都没有看穿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爆炸头真可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.41,0:11:16.66,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦～身为摄影师的血在沸腾
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.83,0:11:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请务必让我帮你们拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.23,0:11:18.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:19.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好  弄个写真集
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.06,0:11:22.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,标题就是「爱之日记2007」  就这么决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.11,0:11:23.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.08,0:11:26.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢  那么就拜托…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:28.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.51,0:11:29.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  难得…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.72,0:11:33.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  无论怎么看都很可疑吧  太可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.39,0:11:34.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玛莉亚小姐太无防备了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.61,0:11:36.25,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,不错  不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要是答应了就会拍个没完了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.36,0:11:41.63,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这样拍起来没完了的话  就休想脱身…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.35,0:11:37.55,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,真不错啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:40.24,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,更加靠近点  靠近点…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:41.61,zhushi,NTP,0,0,0,,再来个吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.81,0:11:43.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.48,0:11:44.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.28,0:11:46.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总之原宿就到此为止  去别的地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.09,0:11:47.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.28,0:11:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.05,0:11:51.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是觉得太麻烦了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.05,0:11:53.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那只是在害羞罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:54.37,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可爱～
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:57.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,因此  两人去了下个约会地点
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.13,0:11:59.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就在此时
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.91,0:12:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐就这么停着笔
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.04,0:12:08.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玛莉亚  茶呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.77,0:12:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对了  现在家里只有我一个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.78,0:12:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,算了  稍微散一下步也能转变心情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.50,0:12:22.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这不是小飒的房间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.82,0:12:25.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且  门还就这么开着…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:30.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  不能无故进入别人房间
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:34.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无论是谁都有隐私啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.40,0:12:35.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  摆脱这种念头了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.82,0:12:43.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这是命运的恶作剧还是思念所致呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.31,0:12:44.16,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笔居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.42,0:12:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这种时候…果然
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.32,0:12:52.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}ボヤボヤしてると置いてっちゃいますよ！{\r}\N再发呆的话就要丢下你了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.13,0:12:57.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fs22}よろこんでついてまいります heart{\r}\N很乐意跟随你  heart
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.15,0:13:00.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.40,0:13:01.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:03.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为了捡掉在地上的笔  实在是情非得已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:04.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.99,0:13:06.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是不可抗力
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.55,0:13:08.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你在向谁辩解啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.63,0:13:11.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而…而且小飒也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.32,0:13:13.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出去的时候至少应该锁门
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:16.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,桌…桌子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.10,0:13:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这…这里就是…小飒一直坐着学习的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.73,0:13:27.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  我…我在做什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.98,0:13:33.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我也真是的  只是进个男生的房间  在动摇什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.40,0:13:37.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不过有点不舒服了  就睡一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.67,0:13:41.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真的只是身体不舒服而已哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,已经够了哦  不用找什么借口了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.31,0:13:53.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我做这种事情究竟想怎么样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.36,0:13:55.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不行  不行  感觉头晕了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.69,0:13:57.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快点回去继续画漫画
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.10,0:14:00.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  笔…笔…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.73,0:14:01.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,笔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:02.96,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.39,0:14:07.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,莫非是十几岁的男生必定会收藏起来的满载女体的那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.46,0:14:09.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  小飒已经有了我还有这种东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.74,0:14:10.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不是  小飒他不会…不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可是  作为「主人」与「恋人」的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.13,0:14:20.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,美妙的…兄贵？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.42,0:14:21.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来他是这种爱好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.83,0:14:26.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,无法理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  我藏起来的宝贝被大小姐发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.63,0:14:33.18,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,原来你有那种爱好啊  这家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.03,0:14:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  这是浅草吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.72,0:14:39.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  坐地铁只需要三十分
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.40,0:14:41.24,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是中吉  小飒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.69,0:14:43.00,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…还是不要问了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.44,0:14:45.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好热  好热…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:46.46,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请慢慢吃
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.38,0:14:48.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.84,0:14:49.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快看这个
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.26,0:14:50.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.25,0:14:52.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  好可爱啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.09,0:15:02.55,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（穿水手服的是「初音岛」的芳乃樱）
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.86,0:15:06.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  一不留神就享受起了平常的约会了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.59,0:15:09.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我真是的  还拉小飒的衣袖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:11.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么做出这么大胆的事…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:15.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,客人  要坐一下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.25,0:15:18.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,给你们算便宜点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.31,0:15:19.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,人…人力车？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.78,0:15:21.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们会把现今最流行约会地点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.95,0:15:23.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向你们逐一介绍的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.18,0:15:25.89,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,可以作为漫画的资料呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:27.51,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.65,0:15:28.53,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:29.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.84,0:15:30.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请交给我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:33.61,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.77,0:15:36.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒啊  出发
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.96,0:15:37.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好快
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.08,0:15:39.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好强的脚力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.37,0:15:41.64,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,向着加固两人之间爱情的约会地点
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.89,0:15:42.65,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,前进！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.38,0:15:50.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住在江户川区东小岩的田中家的约翰很擅长算术
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.79,0:15:52.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…约会地点？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.49,0:15:55.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,而且很干脆的算错了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.42,0:15:57.52,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来是寄生虫的博物馆
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:16:01.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这个在约会的时候看到的话会怎么想…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.13,0:16:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这个…有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.73,0:16:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,像寄生虫一样互相寄生着幸福地生活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.60,0:16:07.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是都内非常有名的灵异地点
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.84,0:16:10.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,运气好的话能看到从天花板掉下来的女性幽灵…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.71,0:16:12.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请请请…请不要带我们来可怕的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.87,0:16:14.06,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…夏天的话也许还可以
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:18.28,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（这是动画制作公司「シナジーSP(SynergySP)」参加制作NDS游戏\N「ハヤテのごとく! ボクがロミオでロミオがボクで」）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.53,0:16:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最后是这里
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.73,0:16:18.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,制作出了许多有趣的动画的公司
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:20.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,月岛星璃的人也来过哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:20.72,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（「きらりん☆レボリューション」的主人公）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.83,0:16:22.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,最后是这里啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.79,0:16:25.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,要好好吃饭和保证睡眠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.84,0:16:28.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,如何
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:30.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是感觉到浪漫了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:33.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说…结果是送回原处了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.31,0:16:35.62,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  真是宝贵的经验啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.88,0:16:38.12,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  玛莉亚小姐这么说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.27,0:16:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  数码相机被…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.75,0:16:45.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,快啦快啦  快点亲一个
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.57,0:16:45.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:47.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,缠人！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.60,0:16:50.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,墨田的海就是我的海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,船要开了～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.71,0:16:52.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要坐  我们要坐！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:54.99,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}点心制作教师
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:54.99,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}讲师  Grazie牧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:54.99,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}第27回
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.06,0:16:54.99,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7}注满爱的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.68,0:16:56.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.81,0:16:59.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不愧是我啊  做得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.52,0:17:02.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下决心来点心教室真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.67,0:17:04.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  真是太华丽了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:06.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,也没那么好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.70,0:17:07.19,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,（小飒  love）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.23,0:17:07.19,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,只要有爱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.35,0:17:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,太豪华了  Grazie
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.55,0:17:14.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,第一次看到有学生能做出那么出色的蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.54,0:17:16.34,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真不敢当  Grazie
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.31,0:17:19.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,输了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.86,0:17:24.29,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总算逃出来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:25.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.59,0:17:26.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,…哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:28.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,唔呀  等等！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.77,0:17:30.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们已经把气氛搞得那么高涨了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.58,0:17:32.90,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,居然还不亲一个  快亲一个！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.13,0:17:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还…还在追
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.74,0:17:36.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是纠缠不休的家伙啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.04,0:17:37.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,照这个形式
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.23,0:17:42.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,看来她们几个要是拍不到我和玛莉亚的吻…吻照
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.62,0:17:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,还是会穷追不舍的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.56,0:17:47.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为…为了保护玛莉亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.20,0:17:52.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,让我来告诉你船的性能好坏并不是战斗力差距的决定因素！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.20,0:17:52.41,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（原话出自夏亚之口：MSの性能の違いが戦力の決定的差でないことを教えてやる!\N(我来告诉你MS性能好坏并不是战斗力差距的决定因素)）
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.12,0:17:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,飞奔吧  青春
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.12,0:17:57.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你的首级我收下了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.81,0:17:59.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别逃了  躲藏也是没用的没用的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:01.14,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:01.14,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（这是捉迷藏游戏惯用的台词）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:02.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别过来！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.39,0:18:04.35,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别…别做傻事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.75,0:18:07.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再接近我的话  我就从这跳下去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:10.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,为…为什么  为何突然这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.74,0:18:11.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了  怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.64,0:18:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是所谓的情侣斗嘴吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.10,0:18:18.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  除了你之外  我还有其他喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.27,0:18:20.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,喜…喜欢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.98,0:18:22.94,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,他是捕金枪鱼船的船员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.51,0:18:25.74,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然一年里有大半年不能相见…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.94,0:18:28.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那…那种男人还是忘记比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.17,0:18:29.71,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.83,0:18:30.41,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.89,0:18:31.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就算不能相见…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.36,0:18:34.32,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样我还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.00,0:18:35.88,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,爱着他的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.52,0:18:39.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎…怎么这样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.19,0:18:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,比起你  比起中鸟  比起大鸟
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.42,0:18:43.40,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是更喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.90,0:18:45.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所以  请忘了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.27,0:18:47.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.23,0:18:47.68,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.33,0:18:50.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.54,0:18:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.83,0:18:55.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.47,0:18:59.58,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大海你这混蛋——！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.88,0:19:00.70,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我们…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.26,0:19:02.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,难道是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.99,0:19:06.43,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎目睹了一个恋爱终结的瞬间…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.02,0:19:08.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哈亚太君好可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:13.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,所谓初恋就是既脆弱又痛彻心扉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.41,0:19:18.48,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,现在就让这个心碎的少年单独待一会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.92,0:19:22.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊  时间会治愈他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.37,0:19:29.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,今天所见的  就把它悄悄保存在我们的心灵深处吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.03,0:19:33.81,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,把恋爱终结留在心灵深处的她们…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.95,0:19:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来  去月岛再去吃一顿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.91,0:19:38.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,赞成～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.27,0:19:43.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之后  就永远没有回忆起今天这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.44,0:19:49.93,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玛莉亚小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.26,0:19:50.98,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.34,0:19:53.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,总算是赶走他们了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.32,0:19:56.21,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,多亏了玛莉亚小姐的倾情演出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:19:57.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不  也没那么厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.71,0:20:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,说回来  那些人到底是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:03.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,忘记吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:05.86,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,反正也不会再见面了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.39,0:20:08.22,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  差不多回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.54,0:20:10.04,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大小姐该等的望眼欲穿了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.22,0:20:10.85,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.61,0:20:12.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.11,0:20:17.44,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒  最后去坐坐那个吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:25.83,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,玛莉亚小姐  今天真是谢谢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:28.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,没什么  我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.74,0:20:30.25,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.77,0:20:34.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,小飒下次能跟真心喜欢的人约会就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.40,0:20:36.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶？哎呀…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.89,0:20:40.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这里应该怎么回答是好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.84,0:20:41.60,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.58,0:20:43.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下次把小凪带来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.39,0:20:45.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,三人约会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.10,0:20:47.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  是的  一定
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.78,0:20:50.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  最后拍一张
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.70,0:21:03.02,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样  大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.34,0:21:05.36,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是觉得我们拍得很好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.72,0:21:09.59,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,其它还有许多在原宿啊  浅草这些能成为资料的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.95,0:21:11.38,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,一定能画出好漫画的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.39,0:21:14.30,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是这么觉得…的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.59,0:21:16.87,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开…开…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.20,0:21:20.97,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,开什么玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.15,0:21:25.28,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,别人痛苦的要死
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.50,0:21:28.03,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,你还笑呵呵的享受约会
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.24,0:21:29.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.99,0:21:33.27,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,大家也一清早邀出男友或女友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.57,0:21:36.01,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,来一次浪漫的约会怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.29,0:21:39.92,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,当然是在有对象的前提下  要有对象啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.61,0:21:42.99,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,话说  不要说这种会引起观看者争吵的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.13,0:21:45.47,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,下集是与中老年的烦恼战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.27,0:23:21.77,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,亘与
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.05,0:23:22.49,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,沙希的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.80,0:23:23.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,管家通讯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.88,0:23:26.33,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哟  我是橘亘
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.65,0:23:27.56,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是贵岛沙希
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.89,0:23:30.78,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,出租录像店橘的主题曲终于制作完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.93,0:23:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,这次正式公开
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.29,0:23:35.09,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶  这个是我们店的主题曲吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.25,0:23:36.67,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,是的  你不知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.88,0:23:40.39,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  歌词里一次都没有出现过「出租录像店橘」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.58,0:23:43.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,那个  就是那个  是店里的印象曲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.98,0:23:45.84,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  这曲子不出租  请务必购买…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.95,0:23:47.57,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  少爷  不能再说下去了…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.68,0:23:48.76,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哦  说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.40,0:23:50.20,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.37,0:23:56.07,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  居然梦见退休后成为巴西咖啡园的庄园主悠闲隐居
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.22,0:23:57.79,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,真是个奇怪的梦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.60,0:24:00.15,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,不错啊  想退休便退休如何
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.32,0:24:00.80,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,诶！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.97,0:24:03.17,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,到底是怎么了  克劳斯先生那么失落
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.34,0:24:05.69,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,被小凪劝其退休  很受打击吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.86,0:24:07.54,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我是主人的影子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.70,0:24:10.08,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,在觉得到了对主人起不到任何作用的那一刻
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.18,0:24:11.91,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,我只会安静地消失
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.06,0:24:13.26,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,次回  旋风管家
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.47,0:24:15.23,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,「克劳斯是名字写为仓臼的日本人」
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.40,0:24:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.14,0:24:18.73,zhengwen,NTP,0,0,0,,西乡隆盛的真名其实是隆永哦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.14,0:24:18.73,neta,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}（西乡隆盛：日本的武士薩摩藩士、军人、政治家。 真名西乡隆永、隆盛是他父亲的名字。）